  "id": 5673998232977408,
  "name": "WebGPU: `subgroup_uniformity` feature",
  "summary": "Functionality added to the WebGPU spec after its first shipment in a browser.\n\nAdds a new scope to the uniformity analysis and changes which parts of the language are checked in each to allow subgroup functionality to be considered uniform in more cases.",
